data.description: Come take a look at this newly built (2022) townhome in the gated community of Riverwalk of Melbourne.  As you step inside this home, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area with 9-foot ceilings and tile flooring that runs throughout the first floor. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, kitchen, and dining area. The kitchen has granite countertops and 42-inch upper cabinets for added storage. The wine refrigerator is a nice addition. Upgraded light fixtures and ceiling fans as well as black baseboards and trim add to the overall elegance of the space. Head upstairs to find the master suite, complete with a glass enclosed shower and double vanity. The other two bedrooms are located on this level as well as a loft area perfect for use as a study or reading nook. Many amenities are included in the HOA fee :Heated Pool, Fitness Center, Sauna, Jacuzzi and a Playground. This home features concrete block construction, a concrete tile roof, energy efficient impact-resistant windows and sliding doors,  8-foot high front door, and an 8-foot high sliding door out to the back screened porch. The lush landscaping and brick paver driveway add to the curb appeal. Inside you'll find smart home automation including a Skybell doorbell and a front door and garage door that can be controlled by a phone app.'||chr(10)||'Located in Melbourne, Florida - this townhouse offers easy access to all that the city has to offer. Great schools, shopping, and beautiful beaches are just a short drive away.  Easy access to US 1 and  I-95 make for a quick commute to the Space Center or Orlando area attractions.
